## Stretch Features

### Geometry Mode

Draw a triangle by hand. AI recognizes it, labels points, computes measurements, and can animate proofs.

### Physics Mode

Write equations with units and force diagrams. AI tracks dimensional consistency and can animate vectors, fields, and motion.

### Word Problem Mode

User writes messy natural-language problem text. AI extracts entities, constants, and assumptions — then turns it into structured math on the same page. (Translation engine: reality → solvable form.)

### Video-From-Page

Tap “teach this.” The pad generates a short lesson video from the current page:

- Cleaned visuals
- Step-by-step animation
- Optional voiceover
- Exportable

### Collaborative Mode

Student and tutor edit the same live page. Or student replays the teacher’s reasoning after class.

### Exam Mode

No answer reveal. Legal hints only. Misconception flags enabled. Timer optional.

